> Sports Strange late sequence gives Seattle 13-10 win over Detroit Detroit Lions quarterback Matthew Stafford, right, walks away after talking to Seattle Seahawks quarterback Russell Wilson, left, after the Seahawks beat the Lions 13-10 in an NFL football game, Monday, Oct. 5, 2015, in Seattle.
